Package com.flipkart.bean

Class FlipFitSlotBooking

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.bean.FlipFitSlotBooking
public class FlipFitSlotBooking extends Object
Represents a slot booking in the FlipFit system. This class contains details such as booking ID, user ID, center slot ID, slot date, booking date, status, and payment ID.
